
Outline of XML
- CA type
- size of grid (num cells) [Visualizer has predefined display size for any size grid]


Each type includes its initial state
- CA types (extendable)
    - Percolation
        - blocked
        - percent open (of unblocked) -> rest are percolated

    - Fire
        - empty
        - percent burning

    - Game of Life
        - ??

    - Segregation
        - Similar
        - percent blue ppl
        - percent empty

    - Predator-Prey
        - Percent predator
        - percent empty
        - prey reproduction waiting time
        - predator reproduction waiting time
        - predator initial energy
            ("energy" idea from http://beltoforion.de/article.php?a=wator_simulation)